    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA ensemble achieves the pre-specified acceptance criteria for all three QoIs across both laboratories. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The Test conditions factor falls one gradation below the required level, accepted on the basis of regulatory precedent and the explicitly bounded COU. The Equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed; the team's position that direct lot traceability renders the assessment redundant is noted but not formally encoded as not-applicable. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for a Medium-assurance regulatory submission at modelRiskLevel 3.",
